comments: Herro (MIA) does not place his hand underneath the ball during his dribble.
Melton (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Butler (MIA) and absorbs the contact.
Melton (MEM) cleanly dislodges the ball from Herro (MIA) during his gather at the end of the drive.
Dragic (MIA) engages with Clarke (MEM) but does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position during the rebound.
Dragic (MIA) makes contact with Melton's (MEM) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Brooks (MEM) makes marginal contact with Butler (MIA) as he brushes his arm in an attempt to deflect the inbounds pass.
Brooks (MEM) makes incidental contact to Dragic's (MIA) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Clarke (MEM) grabs Dragic's (MIA) arm and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Dragic (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brooks (MEM) and collapses his arms as he absorbs the contact.
Butler (MIA) commits a take foul on Anderson (MEM).
